body:
## Nathan Beck

#### I am a recent graduate of METIS, a full-stack Ruby on Rails development program taught by [thoughtbot](http://thoughtbot.com/) in Boston.

I have created and contributed to several applications using Ruby, Rails, javascript, jQuery, CSS (using SASS & SCSS) and html. Use the following links to find code samples and repos.

#### [rentR](https://github.com/NateJBeck/RentR)
An AirBnB clone. Really wanted to learn more about [GoogleMaps Javascript API](https://github.com/NateJBeck/RentR/blob/master/app/assets/javascripts/geocoder-simple.js) to render dynamic content, plus try my hand at using some sass styling gems like bourbon and neat to stylize the site.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
